(د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef solsIncl (د‡ : ACCSystem) : د‡.Sols â†’[â„ڑ] د‡.Charges :=\n  MulActionHom.comp د‡.quadSolsIncl د‡.solsInclQuadSols\n\n/-!\nThe inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`.\n-/\n\n/-- The inclusion of `Sols` into `Charges`. -/\ndef so